Most recent update seems to have removed all the grammar/info sections from the lesson (at least in Japanese for english speakers). Previously when you tapped a lesson, a popup came up with a start button below which would start the quiz and 2 buttons top right. One to let you skip the level with a difficult quiz, the other which actually led you to a page that taught you the material of the lesson e.g. grammar, alphabet etc. This latter button has now disappeared in the latest upate!

I love this app + really recommend it but I have 1 question. There used to be a lightbulb icon you could click on & it would tell you information about what you would learn/practice next in each part of the course. I liked using this to write my own notes down for instance. But now it's gone? Will it be brought back? I hope it will. Either way I still think this app is brilliant, and with hardwork and consistency you'll learn any language.
